quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  6,141,Li est Unu establ gxarden trellised untrellised palm arb crops different gust oliv granat! - Frukt est simil dissimilar Mangx their frukt don due alms tag rikolt ne waste anything! Li ne am wasters
